Let's make some things clearer for the noobs. If you have:
250 kb line - you're download speed 15-20 kb
1 Mb line - you're download speed 60-80 kb
2 Mb line - you're download speed 120-140 kb
8 Mb line - you're download speed 480- 560 kb
and so on...
I had a 250 line first,then 1 Mb, then 2Mb and now 8 Mb so i'm speaking from my own experience. The higher you're internet speed connection the more you'll download because you are PAYING for that download speed. Of course, if there aren't many seeders ( which is always the case when a torrent is put up) the speed MAY vary. So please, all the idiots geting their first taste of hormon changes and testosteron, shut the fuck up. Don't BEG for seeders, it is you're own daddy and mommy that haven't PAYED for a faster internet connection. What you are getting here is FREE of charge. My only wish is that it may also be FREE of you're whining, but that's not gonna happen. So once again, please shut the fuck up and get you're emotional bursts under some control. You're comments DON'T matter, they are just annoying.
